metadata.name: The Tree of Life
metadata.description:
"I am pure Wisdom, 
Knowledge runs through my pores,
And like a Spider's Web, I am connected to
Everything that is. 
As the Tree of Life, I give my Seeds to all
of the Awaken Beings,
All the Love and Light for the greater good
And a brand new World, full of wonders and kindness". 
by Siana

Mixed media, painting, acryl on wood, 40 x 76 cm
